#originalTopic=should-marriage-for-same-sex-couples-be-legal
I'm not trying to incite a conflict, but ... don't you have it almost backwards?The couple is in love, and they want a public expression of that love.  The legal benefits are ways for them to be able to practice and reinforce that love.  The benefits aren't the ends.  The expression and practice of love is.